    <p><b>Convection fan motor wear (where equipped)</b>, $240-$420.</p>
    <p><b>Control board lockout</b>, factory reset resolves some; replacement $320-$560.</p>
    <p><b>Temperature sensor drift</b>, $160-$280.</p>
